Package org.omancode.rmt.cellreader

Classes for processing individual cell values in tables.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CellReader<R> A function that takes an Object and returns a value of another type.
 

Class Summary
BooleanReader Converts an object to a Boolean without loss of fidelity.
CellReaders Utility class providing default cell readers.
CharacterReader Converts an object to a Character without loss of fidelity.
DoubleReader Converts an object to a Double without loss of fidelity.
IdentityReader Returns the value read without any processing.
IntegerReader Converts an object to an Integer without loss of fidelity.
MissingValueReader Reader that checks the read value and returns a different value if the read value is missing, ie: null or empty string.
StringReader Converts an object to a String without loss of fidelity.
TokenReader Reader that checks the read value and returns a different value if matches a token.
 

Exception Summary
CellReaderException Runtime exception during cell reading.
 

Package org.omancode.rmt.cellreader Description

Classes for processing individual cell values in tables.
